{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idf6f3fce2-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s58102"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"58102"},"text":"§ 58102.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Default on payment or maintenance of reserves","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Transportation may supervise the number and compensation of all officers and employees of a contractor under the operating-differential subsidy program or a charterer under chapter 575 of this title, receiving an operating-differential subsidy, if the contractor or charterer—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6f3fce3-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s58102/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is in default on a mortgage, note, purchase contract, or other obligation to the Secretary; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6f3fce4-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s58102/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" has not maintained, in a manner satisfactory to the Secretary, all of the reserves provided for in this subtitle.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idf6f3fce5-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/304/s8/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–304, § 8(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-10-06"},"text":"Oct. 6, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/1671"},"text":"120 Stat. 1671","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idf6f3fce6-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5"},"text